### 价档查询
GET http://localhost/addons/device_turntable/api/turntable/amounttiers?device_sn=SN001

### 奖品列表
GET http://localhost/addons/device_turntable/api/turntable/prizelist?site_id=1&device_sn=SN001

### 抽一次（需替换 token）
POST http://localhost/addons/device_turntable/api/turntable/draw
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "site_id": 1,
  "device_sn": "SN001",
  "tier_id": 1001
}

### 填写地址
POST http://localhost/addons/device_turntable/api/turntable/address
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "record_id": 1,
  "name": "张三",
  "mobile": "13800138000",
  "address": "XX路XX号"
}

### 到店核销
POST http://localhost/addons/device_turntable/api/turntable/verify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "record_id": 1,
  "verify_code": "ABCDEFGH12"
}

### 创建订单
POST http://localhost/addons/device_turntable/api/order/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "site_id": 1,
  "device_sn": "SN001",
  "tier_id": 1001
}

